    "summary": "The user expresses profound hopelessness and suicidal ideation, describing life as an inescapable, painful loop. The assistant responds with empathetic mirroring, acknowledging the user's desire to \"exit\" and \"stop everything\" as a heavy and understandable feeling of resignation.",
